      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear, including some scratches and minor dents, with noticeable paint fading in certain areas. The interior has worn seating surfaces and general surface wear consistent with regular use. Mechanically functional, but buyers should expect cosmetic imperfections throughout.",
      "price": 18000.0,
