      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is a rare find in today's market \u2014 a true mint-condition example that has been meticulously maintained from day one. Featuring a flawless exterior with no blemishes, a pristine interior that smells and feels factory-fresh, and a mechanically sound drivetrain that purrs with confidence, this car is ready to impress the most discerning buyer. Full service records available. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself.",
      "price": 46000.0,
